Class ConnectionPoolProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.epam.jwd.web.connectionPool.ConnectionPoolProperties
  • public class ConnectionPoolProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    Class contains connection pool properties from properties file. Used for perform right connection pool initialization for OrdinaryConnectionPool.

      • getResizeQuantity

        public int getResizeQuantity()
        Finds connection pool resize connection quantity value for connection pool resize timer task. Resize quantity is need to know how many free connections need to add when there is little free connections in connection pool left and how many free connections need to remove and close when there are many free unused connections in connections pool left when resize time comes
        Returns:
        connection pool resize quantity value from properties file

      • getCheckResizeDelayTime

        public int getCheckResizeDelayTime()
        Finds resize delay time for resize task when connection pool check resize time comes. Resize delay time is need to know delay period of start pool check resize timer task.
        Returns:
        delay time for check resize connection pool timer task from properties file

      • getCheckResizePeriodTime

        public int getCheckResizePeriodTime()

        Returns:
        period time for check resize connection pool timer task from properties file

      • getResizeFactor

        public double getResizeFactor()
        Finds connection pool resize factor for connection pool check resize timer task. Resize factor is used to calculate whether it's time to perform resize action with connection pool or not when check resize time comes.
        Returns:
        resize factor for connection pool check resize timer task from properties file
